title: Areas for Renewal in Lisbon, Portugal
name: Areas for Renewal in Lisbon, Portugal
description: The map shows areas that need to be renewed in Lisbon. The areas in dark red along river Tejo are occupied by mainly old people, living in dilapidated houses while the areas in dark blue are occupied by high income people. The analysis was done using the Hot spot spatial statistics tool in ArcGis.
